author: lundblad
msg: More developers should work with large working copies...
Reduce memory usage when working with working copies with many directories.
This fixes a leak when upgrading working copies to a new format.
(do_open): Do more work in the subpool, avoiding allocating temporary
resources in a pool that we know will be long-lived.
